<h2>Google Business Profile for Financial Advisors</h2>
<p>Your <a href="/blog/optimize-google-business-profile/">Google Business Profile</a> drives visibility in local map results. 46% of all Google searches have local intent. When a prospect searches "financial advisor near me," the map pack appears first.</p>
<h3>Profile Setup Checklist</h3>
<ul>
<li>[ ] Primary category: "Financial Planner" or "Financial Consultant"</li>
<li>[ ] Secondary categories: Investment Service, Retirement Planning Center, Tax Consultant</li>
<li>[ ] Complete business description (750 characters, include city, services, and credentials)</li>
<li>[ ] Office hours (include appointment-only availability)</li>
<li>[ ] Phone number (trackable local number preferred)</li>
<li>[ ] Website URL pointing to your homepage</li>
